206
00:39:30,511 --> 00:39:31,511
<font color=#FFFF00>Entre.</font>

207
00:40:57,144 --> 00:40:58,211
<font color=#FFFF00>Perdão.</font>

208
00:40:58,212 --> 00:41:01,384
<font color=#FFFF00>Ouvi seu carro,
