210
00:41:03,313 --> 00:41:05,201
<font color=#FFFF00>Foi culpa da minha mão mole.</font>

211
00:41:05,202 --> 00:41:06,611
<font color=#FFFF00>Que desperdício!</font>

212
00:41:06,612 --> 00:41:08,125
