213
00:41:08,125 --> 00:41:10,042
<font color=#FFFF00>Via Condotti, Roma.</font>

214
00:41:10,042 --> 00:41:12,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Deixe-me secá-los.</font>

215
00:41:12,311 --> 00:41:14,207
<font color=#FFFF00>Couro italiano, Glenda.</font>

216
00:41:14,208 --> 00:41:18,707
<font color=#FFFF00>Vale a pena tentar.
