232
00:42:20,976 --> 00:42:22,906
<font color=#FFFF00>Sentei lá, bem quietinho.</font>

233
00:42:23,793 --> 00:42:26,080
<font color=#FFFF00>E, logo antes de atirar,</font>

234
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:29,287
<font color=#FFFF00>apareceu mais um.</font>

235
00:42:29,750 --> 00:42:31,125
<font color=#FFFF00>E então, um terceiro.</font>

236
00:42:31,126 --> 00:42:32,286
<font color=#FFFF00>Um quarto.</font>

237
00:42:32,524 --> 00:42:34,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Uma família desses malditos.</font>

238
00:42:37,113 --> 00:42:38,331
<font color=#FFFF00>Euros.</font>

239
00:42:38,332 --> 00:42:41,892
<font color=#FFFF00>Meias brancas?
